[2026-07-02T01:15:40.994Z] [INFO] [stderr] ## Features
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.994Z] [INFO] [stderr] A fully client-side, offline-first personal IELTS study system. Track vocabulary, reading, listening, writing, speaking, grammar, and mock tests — all in your browser with no backend required. Includes a Chrome extension for collecting learning material from any webpage.
