[2026-07-02T01:15:40.994Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Vocabulary Management** — Add, tag, filter, and review words with SM-2 spaced repetition
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.994Z] [INFO] [stderr] 
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Mock Test Tracker** — Log mock test scores and track band progress over time
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Progress Analytics** — Charts and stats for study days, hours, skill balance, and band trends
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Skill Tracking** — Log reading, listening, writing, and speaking practice sessions
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **AI Tutor Chat** — Messenger-style AI assistant with proactive local messages
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Import/Export** — Full JSON backup and restore with merge/replace modes
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Learning Journey Engine** — Weakness detection, review scheduling, next-best-action recommendations
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Browser Extension** — Collect vocabulary, sentences, and articles from any webpage
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Exercise Generator** — AI-powered and rule-based exercise generation
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **Content Library** — Built-in IELTS content with versioned updates
[2026-07-02T01:15:40.995Z] [INFO] [stderr] - **PWA Support** — Install as standalone app, works offline
